Set up instructions

Install node (If you don't already have it)
	brew update
	brew install node

Install and setup MongoDB
	brew install mongodb
	
	Create data directory
		mkdir -p /data/db

	Set permissions for data directory 
		chown -R username /data/db

	Run mongodb
		mongod

	Before running, may need to add /data/db to your path
		PATH="$PATH":/data/db/

To build application and run it
	grunt - for building
	grunt serve - for preview
	grunt serve:dist - for preview of built app

See https://github.com/DaftMonk/generator-angular-fullstack for more details 
	
